      <title>万科利润暴跌46% 誓言削减债务140亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/china-vanke-profit-tumbles-46-vows-to-cut-debt-by-14-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[万科公司去年的利润跌幅超过分析师预期，并誓言将债务削减近 140 亿美元，因为这家陷入困境的开发商在旷日持久的房地产危机中试图避免违约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/china-vanke-profit-tumbles-46-vows-to-cut-debt-by-14-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 12:47:21 GMT</pubDate>
