      <title>为委内瑞拉石油预订的油轮现已滞留数月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/tankers-booked-for-venezuelan-oil-have-now-been-stuck-for-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一批本应从委内瑞拉装载石油的油轮在该国海岸闲置了数月，这让一些在制裁放松后重返该国石油贸易的贸易商感到头疼——以及船主的发薪日。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/tankers-booked-for-venezuelan-oil-have-now-been-stuck-for-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 12:40:39 GMT</pubDate>
