      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/powell-juices-bets-in-bond-market-on-inflation-with-tilt-to-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔越来越注重保护就业市场，这鼓励了一大批债券交易员押注通胀率将保持在高位。]]></description>
